DISCLAIMER

This dataset is provided for educational and research purposes only. It is not 
an official religious authority. Always verify Hadith with trusted scholarly 
sources. The texts are compiled from public references.

The dataset maintainers make no representations or warranties regarding the 
accuracy, completeness, or authenticity of the Hadith texts. Users are 
responsible for verifying the content independently.
